{"tid":486697,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[將超越OLED/QLED？] 三星 Micro LED 電視傳 2018 年 CES 亮相","createTime":"2017-12-02T05:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T06:45:17.000Z","uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0fab556ece1de6896dfc99876f4689e10a765c30","tid":486697,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T05:45:39.000Z","msg":"蘋果（Apple Inc.）積極布局 Micro LED 螢幕，日前還傳出正在跟台積電解決瓶頸問題，而三星電子（Samsung Electronics）也不落人後，傳出打算在 2018 年 1 月的美國拉斯維加斯消費性電子展（CES）上，發表一款 Micro LED 電視。<br />\n<br />\nZDNet 24 日報導，三星的 Micro LED 電視螢幕將達到 150 吋，會在明年稍晚正式上市，瞄準的是家庭劇院市場。<br />\n<br />\n想要製造縮小版的 LED，難度相當高。Micro LED 螢幕使用的 LED，尺寸不到 100 微米，每顆 LED 晶片可做為一個畫素，優點是耗電量低，也不會有 OLED 的殘影（burn-in）問題。若採用塑膠製基板，則會具有可撓性。智慧型手機需要更加微小的 LED 晶片，因此應用上還得再等一陣子。<br />\n<br />\n三星發言人不願對此做出評論。Sony 曾在 2012 年搶先展示了一款 55 吋的 Micro LED 電視和多款原型機，但至今還無法商業化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2017/11/24/samsung-micro-led-tv-2018-ces/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2Fsamsung-micro-led-tv-2018-ces%2F&d=GAyoW2IVBjKVGnhFwJyaoAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=30adceb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2017/11/24/samsung-micro-led-tv-2018-ces/</a>"},{"pid":"154b177b66953b8d252324d0b71896ae3e07fdde","tid":486697,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:21:05.000Z","msg":"QLED 只係LCD變種"},{"pid":"9772382a9abc0007e7634ff4ee437803c2b61051","tid":486697,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>QLED 只係LCD變種</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/02/142142_b7b69eec6c34f16ddf066b18cea85dc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F142142_b7b69eec6c34f16ddf066b18cea85dc8.jpg&h=3d051acd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0832e90badc224107cd1050ad1166c6196938efe","tid":486697,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T06:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}